                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Acting Secretary of State <persName type="from"
                            >Adee</persName> to Minister <persName type="to">Wilson</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-09-17">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 17, 1906</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(The minister is informed, relative to immigration to South Carolina, that the
                    advance of passage money to an alien does not violate the contract-labor law,
                    but that an alien must prove affirmatively that he will not become a public
                    charge and submit to examination as to other legal requirements.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
